OL,3,C'I was at death's door': How a
OL,4,Cshoplifter broke a 20-year cycle of
OL,5,Ccrime
OL,7,FA man from Carlisle says more needs to
OL,8,Fbe done to tackle the root cause of
OL,9,Fshoplifting in Cumbria.
OL,11,FNow three years sober, Danny Woodburn
OL,12,Fbattled with addiction and substance
OL,13,Fabuse for most of his adult life.
OL,15,FThe reformed shoplifter from Barrow
OL,16,Fsays his crimes were fuelled by
OL,17,Faddiction - and his life became a
OL,18,F"revolving door" of substances and
OL,19,Fprison.
