OL,3,C'I was at death's door': How a
OL,4,Cshoplifter broke a 20-year cycle of
OL,5,Ccrime
OL,7,FWith his criminal past now behind him,
OL,8,FDanny is sharing his story as he
OL,9,Fbegins a new chapter in Carlisle,
OL,10,Fhoping to inspire others to follow in
OL,11,Fhis footsteps.
OL,13,FThe 41-year-old explained that his
OL,14,Foffending began during his teenage
OL,15,Fyears with "petty theft", slowly
OL,16,Fescalating to stealing cars and other
OL,17,Fmore serious crimes.
OL,19,FHe says much of his motivation was the
OL,20,Fdesperate need for money to fund his
OL,21,Fdependency.
