OL,3,C'I was at death's door': How a
OL,4,Cshoplifter broke a 20-year cycle of
OL,5,Ccrime
OL,7,F"When you're dependent on alcohol, it
OL,8,Fmakes you physically ill," he
OL,9,Fexplained. "You can't function like a
OL,10,Fnormal person. I was more bothered
OL,11,Fabout not having a seizure (from
OL,12,Fwithdrawals)."
OL,14,FReflecting on his past, he said he was
OL,15,Fa "person that I didn't know, didn't
OL,16,Frecognise, and I hated it. You know, I
OL,17,Fhate myself. I hate being in my own
OL,18,Fskin."
