OL,3,C'I was at death's door': How a
OL,4,Cshoplifter broke a 20-year cycle of
OL,5,Ccrime
OL,7,FThree years ago, while in prison,
OL,8,FDanny says he was given a wake-up call
OL,9,Fby the police.
OL,11,F"They approached me and said, 'Danny,
OL,12,Fif you go about drinking the way you
OL,13,Fare, I will just let you know you're
OL,14,Fgoing to get arrested again.' And they
OL,15,Fwere right," he recalled.
OL,17,F"They said, 'If you want sobriety and
OL,18,Fclean time, come to The Well.' And
OL,19,Fthat's what I did."
