OL,3,C'I was at death's door': How a
OL,4,Cshoplifter broke a 20-year cycle of
OL,5,Ccrime
OL,7,FDanny reached out for support and
OL,8,Fjoined The Well Communities in
OL,9,FCarlisle in January 2023. He says it
OL,10,Fwas a "life-saving treatment" and
OL,11,Fdescribes the organisation as "the
OL,12,Fambulance" with the key workers "the
OL,13,Fparamedics.
OL,15,FThree years on, the charity that
OL,16,Frescued him from addiction has
OL,17,Fprovided him with the opportunity of a
OL,18,Fsecure role, serving as a 'Grow Your
OL,19,FOwn' key worker.
