OL,4,Cshoplifter broke a 20-year cycle of
OL,5,Ccrime
OL,7,F"I put some extra money in and extra
OL,8,Ffood in the food bank," he said. "I
OL,9,Fcan't make up for what I did, but I
OL,10,Fcan try to make amends in any way I
OL,11,Fcan."
OL,13,FHe hopes his work can help to lift
OL,14,Fothers out of the dark hole of
OL,15,Faddiction.
